snippet.title: Warhammer: Chaosbane - Wood Elf (ESRB)
snippet.description:
Play the swift Wood Elf Scout Elessa, and fire arrows that pierce the enemy ranks. 

Crusade across the Fantasy Battles universe with up to four friends in local and online co-op. Warhammer: Chaosbane is coming to Xbox One, PS4 and PC on June 4th 2019.

Pre-order now for access to the beta in April!
